{"id": 2354, "genre": 1001, "title": "那些流行的“经典名著当代解读”，你见过哪些特别跑偏的套路？", "description": "《红楼梦》，又名《如何在豪门宅斗中升级打怪》。（题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 572, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201805171837076PF0rphLMVEB3yDz.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-19T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 293283, "content": "曾祖母为什么叫作者汉子…", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1295908}, {"id": 293284, "content": "把《一个陌生女人的来信》概括成渣男痴女大联欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164756}, {"id": 293288, "content": "四大名著就差三国演义了，请帮帮它", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775101}, {"id": 293298, "content": "《钢铁是怎样炼成的》三段恋情", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1375231}, {"id": 293304, "content": "从好好一部《资本论》到某主义中国化的最新成果", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875173}, {"id": 282297, "content": "用“如何与领导相处”解读《水浒传》的情节", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 282298, "content": "给《红楼梦》里的人物贴上“玻璃心”“心机女”之类的标签", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 282299, "content": "把“你是什么类型的员工”套在《西游记》的几个主角身上", "image": null, "praise_count": 145, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 282300, "content": "把《简爱》概括成“出轨”“脚踏两只船”的故事", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 293309, "content": "大部分名著都被总结为“渣男劈腿贱女出轨”", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1406417}, {"id": 293314, "content": "四大名著怎么了！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137701}, {"id": 293319, "content": "从卖草鞋转行的艰辛创业路", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1406583}, {"id": 293320, "content": "丰乳肥臀只见丰乳不见肥臀", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115890}, {"id": 293323, "content": "很多的偏见在于时代以及地域的不同导致的价值观的差异，而很多人又不会去了解当时社会情况", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952312}, {"id": 293324, "content": "拿四大名著当历史讲", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346364}, {"id": 293325, "content": "白话文只适合白话的时候用，不能书面话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384411}, {"id": 293326, "content": "《三国演义》兄弟间只有基情", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334651}, {"id": 293330, "content": "说《傲慢与偏见》是小言的开山鼻祖，是一部富二代扶贫史，伊丽莎白是玛丽苏，是凤凰女……", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1375899}, {"id": 293331, "content": "《金瓶梅》又作《中国房事百科全书》", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316254}, {"id": 293333, "content": "拿《三国演员》里人物成败原因，来套在职场人身上", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711174}, {"id": 293335, "content": "《笑傲江湖》都被解读的令狐冲和东方不败爱的死去活来了～", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711174}, {"id": 293341, "content": "被改编到绝望的《西游记》啊，孙悟空被塑造成众多女性的“理想情人”，师徒四人性别不定，时男时女，被情节被爱情化。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1397924}, {"id": 293344, "content": "在企业里，唐僧师徒四人你最想开除谁？然后还有个大部分人认为的标准答案：沙僧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904294}, {"id": 293345, "content": "看不懂经典隐含的社会批判，只盯着些套路去解读的标题党", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923997}]}